    | Regulation cross-checked
  h3.heading-medium
    | The regulation with ID
    =<> "'#{regulation.base_regulation_id}'"
    | and name
    =<> "'#{regulation.legal_id}'"
    | has been submitted for approval.

= render "workbaskets/create_regulation/workflow_screens_parts/status_pages/next_step_links", mode: "cross_checked"
